commit.message:
feat(pipeline): search_intent, url_slug, secondary_keywords, entities + SERP cache

- gemini_adapter: add search_intent field to SERPAnalysis; SERP prompt requests it
- anthropic_adapter: add url_slug to GeneratedArticle; parse URL_SLUG: after META_DESCRIPTION:;
  add secondary_keywords/entities params to generate_article + generate_outline;
  expand style_instructions (storytelling/how_to/informative/persuasive/technical/academic)
  and list_instructions (light/extensive)
- openai_adapter: consume search_intent in serp_block; add secondary_keywords/entities params
- content_pipeline: Redis SERP/research cache (24h TTL) with graceful degradation;
  add url_slug to PipelineResult; wire secondary_keywords/entities through all adapters
- schemas/content: add secondary_keywords/entities fields with cap_list validator;
  expand VALID_WRITING_STYLES to 10 values; expand VALID_LIST_USAGES to 5 values
- articles.py: pass secondary_keywords/entities through background task to pipeline;
  store url_slug in seo_analysis["suggested_slug"]; sync _VALID_* sets with schema
- admin_blog.py: add secondary_keywords/entities to BlogGenerateRequest;
  add url_slug to BlogGenerateResponse
- frontend: add secondary_keywords/entities to GenerateArticleInput and admin blog types;
  add UI inputs on articles/new + admin/blog/new; display suggested slug on admin page

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
